The '''Rationalist Party''' was a political party on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]] that advocated for liberation of the planet and free trade. Led by [[Seti Ashgad/Legends|Seti Ashgad]] and secretly supported by [[Q-Varx]], they engaged in attacks on [[Theran]] outposts on the planet.

